reviewText: I love this movie and I hope to own this product at some point in the future I watched this movie online more time then the other super sental movie a real life god or goddess bringing the  first yellow kirenger from himitsu sental gorenger back from the you know where since Mose people are a ware of what he did the second kirenger is still around to fight or a third or fourth had to been in the time up against the space empire zangyack this also feature some stuff in the product in self

I absolutely love watching this movie. The Only downside is that there no english subtitles on when I watch it. Thats okay though, the good thing is that you can pretty much tell what everyone is saying if you use your imagination. Besides you don't need subtitles to watch a fun fight. Always remember two things though when buying any region dvd. Make sure you have the right all region dvd player & check the language/subtitles out first. You should be good if you do.
